 Oluremi Tinubu  Speaking during the 26th Town Hall meeting under her Youth Empowerment and Skills Acquisition Scheme (YESAS) held in Apapa yesterday, the lawmaker said, “As Nigeria prepares for the 2019 general elections, we must begin to envision a better Nigeria by fulfilling our civic responsibility. We should ensure that only those who mean well for us are burdened with the task of leading us. Every adult citizen must as a matter of urgency collect their PVC.” To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .